{
  "stem": "8916.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, before-- when-- when the last transport was being made-- and we always knew when this was going to happen, because all these special troops came and surrounded the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was just before the ghetto was liquidated, in '43.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we knew the-- the modus operandi by that time, so we knew that something was up.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father was already off to the factory and-- with his working group.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my-- Aviva was-- my sister was already at her working group.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother and I were the only ones left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the plan was-- my mother was planning that I was going to hide.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was going to hide someplace.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because at this point, there was no chance of being exempted from the transport.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in between our two buildings where we lived, there was a-- in the courtyard, there was a small-- small building.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, boy, we-- the brush maker lived there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But above that was a small attic, but it didn't look like it would have an attic, because it was sort of like a lean-to in between-- in the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when we were small kids, we used to play there, and crawl in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a little opening on the side, on the very side of the building.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not very visible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my mother decided that that's-- that's where I was going to hide with two of my friends who also lived in the building.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were-- they belonged to the shoemaker who lived there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Birch.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I used to hang around the shoemaker's house quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I had some other friends also that age from-- from another building.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
